Usage: resetModifiedBudget [-help] -pin <string> [-view <string>] {-ptn <string> | -inst <string>} [-setup  | -hold  ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-hold                   # reset hold information (bool, optional)
-inst <string>          # hierarchical instance for which manual budgets would
                        # be reset (string, required)
-pin <string>           # pin to be reset, use * for all pins
                        # (string, required)
-ptn <string>           # partition for which manual budgets would be reset
                        # (string, required)
-setup                  # reset setup information (bool, optional)
-view <string>          # reset modified budgets for a specific view only
                        # (string, optional)